headline.main: Town Grieving After Mother, 4 Children Die in House Fire
headline.print_headline: Town Grieving After Mother, 4 Children Die in House Fire

lead_paragraph: Laura Muir led an impressive final day for Britain at the European indoor athletics championships with her second gold medal of the three-day event after winning the 3,000-meter race on Sunday.
